OL,3,C'It's taken us 26 years to get here':
OL,4,COmagh bomb inquiry opens
OL,6,F"It has taken us 26 years to get here
OL,7,Fand we're just delighted," said
OL,8,FMichael Gallagher, whose son Aiden was
OL,9,Fkilled in the bombing.
OL,11,FThe names of all those killed were
OL,12,Fread out during proceedings and those
OL,13,Fin the hearing room stood for a
OL,14,Fminute's silence in their memory.
OL,16,FIn his opening statement, Lord
OL,17,FTurnbull said the pain of bereavement
OL,18,Fand trauma caused by the dissident
OL,19,Frepublican bomb attack spread beyond
OL,20,FOmagh and Northern Ireland to families
OL,21,Ffrom England and Spain.
