OL,6,FHe also said the attack, which came
OL,7,Fjust months after the signing of the
OL,8,FBelfast/Good Friday Agreement, caused
OL,9,F"outrage and consternation across
OL,10,Fnational boundaries and across
OL,11,Fcontinents".
OL,13,F"Condemnation was expressed by the
OL,14,FPrime Minister of the United Kingdom
OL,15,Fand the Taoiseach of the Republic of
OL,16,FIreland, other world leaders,
OL,17,Fcommunity leaders, religious leaders
OL,18,Fand political leaders all joined with
OL,19,Fthem in expressing the unforgivable
OL,20,Fnature of what had occurred," he said.
