OL,6,FLord Turnbull said the inquiry will
OL,7,Fundertake its task rigorously and
OL,8,Ffearlessly, and emphasised the
OL,9,F"defining character of the inquiry
OL,10,Fmust be its independence".
OL,12,FHe said "the value which the inquiry
OL,13,Fattaches to its independence means
OL,14,Fthat it will not be amenable to
OL,15,Finfluence from any government or from
OL,16,Fany state agency".
