OL,6,F"It will not allow itself to be
OL,7,Fdeflected from its purpose by the
OL,8,Fdifficulties which may lie in its way
OL,9,Fon account of the passage of time or
OL,10,Fthe volume and complexity of
OL,11,Fmaterials," he said.
OL,13,FLord Turnbull also told the hearing
OL,14,Fthat he will approach the task with an
OL,15,Fopen mind, and "will assess the
OL,16,Fevidence which is heard both fairly
OL,17,Fand reasonably".
