OL,6,F"I will do so without any preformed
OL,7,Fview or impression as to whether the
OL,8,Fatrocity could or could not have been
OL,9,Fprevented," he added.
OL,11,FBereaved families expressed hope as
OL,12,Fthey arrived for the hearing after
OL,13,Fdecades of campaigning for a public
OL,14,Finquiry into the atrocity.
OL,16,FMichael Gallagher said today's hearing
OL,17,Fwill be the first time since 1998 that
OL,18,Fall of the bereaved families,
OL,19,Fincluding those caught up in the blast
OL,20,Ffrom Spain, will come together.
