OL,3,C'It's taken us 26 years to get here':
OL,4,COmagh bomb inquiry opens
OL,6,FSpeaking as he arrived at the Strule
OL,7,FArts Centre on Tuesday morning, Mr
OL,8,FGallagher said it had taken a long
OL,9,Ftime to get here.
OL,11,FHe said: "One of the sad ironies is
OL,12,Fthat when I got up this morning and
OL,13,Fsaw the sunshine, it was exactly the
OL,14,Fsame on August 15 1998. It was one of
OL,15,Fthe most beautiful days of that year.
OL,17,F"It's good to be here. It's a long
OL,18,Ftime but we are where we want to be
OL,19,Fand we just have to wait and see where
OL,20,Fthis inquiry takes us.
OL,26,@sD@JOUyD@AOU
