OL,6,F"Every morning I waken up and still
OL,7,Fpinch myself, I can't believe that
OL,8,Fwe're there."
OL,10,FStanley McCombe, who lost his wife,
OL,11,FAnn, in the bombing, said he had great
OL,12,Ffaith in Lord Turnbull and his legal
OL,13,Fteam.
OL,15,F"After years of hard labour we're
OL,16,Fhopeful, we're very very hopeful," he
